  "remarks": "Nshan Galustyan is a Russian propagandist, president of the Federation of Military and Tactical Games and a member of the management of the All-Russian children’s and youth military-patriotic movement “Yunarmiya”, a Russian paramilitary organisation subject to Union restrictive measures. He is a long-term supporter of President Vladimir Putin and his policies, and has been using his popularity to spread the messages and narratives of Kremlin propaganda.",
